HEADWORD: Stinkball
<hw>Stink"ball`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A composition of
substances which in combustion emit a suffocating odor; -- used formerly
in naval warfare.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

